A Magic: The Gathering life counter app for the Pebble watch.  

Instructions:
Up - removes 1 life from the top player's counter
Up long press - adds 1 life to the top player's counter and continues adding until the button is released
Down - removes 1 life from the bottom player's counter
Down long press - adds 1 life to the bottom player's counter and continues adding until the button is released
Select - start/reset (and stop) the timer
Select long press - resets both life counters to 20
